hadiths[26]{hadithnumber,text}:
2044,"Hasan-bin- Muslim ne Taaus se khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : main eidul-fitr ki Namaz mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam), Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath hazir hua hun. ye sab khutbey se pahley Namaz padhtey they phir khutba detey they aik baar Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( buland jagah se) nichey aaey aisa mehsus hota hai ke main ( ab bhi) aapko dekh raha hun jab aap apne hath se mardon ko bitha rahe they phir unke darmyan mein se rasta banatey huey aagey badhey yahan tak ke aurton ke qareeb tashrif ley aaey aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath they aap ne ( Quran ka ye hissey tilawat ( farmaya; ''aey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! jab aap ke paas momin auratein is baat par bait karne ke liye aaein ke wo Allah Taala ke sath kisi cheez ko Sharik nahi banaygii.'' aap ne ye aayat tilawat farmai yahan tak ke is se farigh huey phir farmaya, tum is par qaaim ho? to aik aurat ne ( jabke ( aapko iske ilawa unmein se aur kisi ne jawab nahi diya kaha : haan aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) !.  us waqt pata nahi chal raha tha ke wo kon hai? aap ne farmaya, tum sadqa karo.  is par Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna kapda phaila diya phir kehney lagey lao tum sab par mere maan-baap qurbaan hon ! to wo apne badey-badey chhalley aur anguthiyan Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein dalney lageii."
2045,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha : ham se Ayub ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha maine Ata se suna unhon-ne kaha maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein shahadat deta hun, aap ne Namaz eid khutbe se pahley padhi phir aap ne khutba diya phir aap ne dekha ke aap ne aurton ko (apni baat ( nahi sunai to aap unke paas aaey aur unko yad dahaanii ( talqeen ( farmai aur unhein nasihat ki aur sadqa karne ka hukm diya aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) apna kapda phailaey huey they koi aurat (is kapdey mein) anguthi phainktii thi (koii halqey daar zewar ( chhalley, baaliyaan, kadey, kangan (aur koi dusri cheezein dalti thi."
2046,Hammad aur Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
2047,ibne-Juraij ne kaha : hamein Ata ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di kaha : maine un ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-fitr ke din (namaz ke liye) khadey huey phir Namaz padhai chunanche aap ne khutbey se pahley Namaz se shuruaat ki phir logon ko khitab farmaya. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( khutbe se) farigh huey to ( chabootrey se) utar kar aurton ke paas aaey unhein tazkeer w nasihat ki jabke aap Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke bazu ka sahara liye huey they aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) apna kapda phailaey huey they auratein usmein sadqa daal rahi thin. (ibne-Juraij ne kaha : ( maine Ata se puchha fitr ke din ka sadqa ( daal rahi thin ? ( unhon-ne kaha : nahi us waqt ( apna ( sadqa kar rahi thin (koii aurat chhallaa dalti thi (isi tarah eik baad eik doosri) daal rahi thin aur daal rahi thin. maine Ata se ( phir ( puchha : kya ab bhi imam ke liye lazim hai ke jab ( mardon ke khutbey se) farigh ho to aurton ko talqeen aur nasihat karey? unhon-ne kaha : haan mujhey apni zindagi ki qism ! ye un par) Aaiz shuda ( haq hai unhein kya ho gaya hai ke wo aisa nahi kartey.
2048,abdul-Malik-bin-abi Sulaiman ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : main eid ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein hazir hua aap ne khutbey se pahley azan aur takbeer ke baghair Namaz se shuruaat ki phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ka sahara lekar khadey huey Allah ke taqwa ka hukm diya uski itaat par ubhaaraa logon ko nasihat ki aur unhein ( Deen ki buniyadi baton ki) yad dahaanii karaai phir chal padey yahan tak ke aurton ke paas aagey (to ( unhein waz (nasihat) w talqeen ( tazkeer ( ki aur farmaya: sadqa karo kyonke tum mein se aksar jahannam ka iindhan hain. aurton ke darmyan se aik bhalii siyaahii maail rukhsaaron wali aurat ne khadey ho kar puchha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kyon ? aap ne farmaya : isliye ke tum shikayat bahut karti ho aur apne rafeeq zindagi ki na-shukri karti ho. ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha is par wo auratein apne zewaraat se sadqa karne lagiin wo Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey main apni baaliyaan aur anguthiyan dalney lagiin .
2049,"saiyedna Ibne-Abbas aur saiyedna Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke azan na eidul-fitr mein hoti thi aur na eidul-azha mein. phir maine unse puchha thodi der ke baad isi baat ko. (ye qaul hai ibne-Juraij rawi ka ( to unhon-ne kaha (yani unke Shekh ata ne) ke khabar di mujhey saiyedna Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke na azan hoti thi eidul-fitr mein jab imam nikalta tha aur na baad iske nikalney ke aur na takbeer hoti, na azan aur na aur kuchh wo din aisa hai ke us din na azan hai na takbeer ."
2050,Muhammad-bin-Raafe ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Razzaq ne hadis sunai kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di kaha : mujhey Ata ne khabar di ke ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ki bait ke shuruat hi mein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki taraf paigham bheja ke eidul-fitr ke din Namaz ( eid (ke liye azan nahi di jati thi lihaza aap uske liye azan na kahalwaaein ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne us din azan na kahlwaaii aur uske sath ye paigham bhi bheja ke khutba Namaz ke baad hai aur) ahade-nabawii aur khilafate raashida mein) aisey hi kya jata tha ( ata ne) kaha : to ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz khutbey se pahley padhai.
2051,Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath eidein ki Namaz aik ya 2 baar padhi hai.
2052,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) eidein ki Namaz khutbey se pahley padhtey they.
2053,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-azha aur eidul-fitr ke din tashrif latey to Namaz se shuruat farmatey aur jab apni Namaz padh letey aur salam phertey to khadey ho jatey logon ki taraf rukh farmatey jabke log apni Namaz padhney ki jagah mein baithey hotey, agar aapko koi lashkar bhejney ki zarurat hoti to uska logon ke samney zikr farmatey aur agar aapko iske siwa koi aur zarurat hoti to unhein iska hukm detey aur farmaya kartey sadqa karo sadqa karo sadqa karo zyada sadqa auratein diya karti thin phir aap wapas ho jatey aur yahi mamool (routine) chalta raha yahan tak ke Marwaan-bin-Hakam ka daur aa gaya mein iske sath hath mein hath daal kar nikla yahan tak ke ham eidgaah mein pahunch gaey to dekha ke Kasir bin Salat ne wahan mitti (ke gaarey (aur enton se member banaya hua tha to achcha Marwan ka hath mujh se khincha tani karne laga jaisey wo mujhey member ki taraf kheench raha ho aur main usey Namaz ki taraf kheench raha hun jab maine uski taraf se ye baat dekhi to maine kaha : Namaz se shuruat (ka masnoon tariqa) kahan hai? usne kaha : aey abu-Saeed ! jo aap jantey hain usey tark kar diya gaya hai maine kaha : hargiz nahi, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! jo main janta hun tum us se behtar tariqa nahi la saktey. padhi. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne teen baar kaha, phir chal diye."
2054,"Muhammad (bin Sirin ( ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aap ne hamein hukm diya. unki murad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se thi. padhi. ke ham dono eidon mein baligha aur parda-nasheen aurton ko ley jaya karein aur aap ne haiz wali aurton ko hukm diya ke wo musalmanon ki Namaz ki jagah se hat kar baithein."
2055,"Aasim ahwal ne Hafsa binte- Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein dono eidon mein nikalney ka hukm diya jata tha, parda nasheen aur do-sheeza ko bhi. unhon-ne kaha : haiz wali auratein bhi niklengi aur logon ke peechhey rahengi aur logon ke sath takbeer kahengi."
2056,"Hisham ne Hafsa bin Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya ke ham eidul-fitr aur eidul-azha mein aurton ko bahar nikalein, dosheeza, haaiza aur parda nashini aurton ko bahar nikalein, lekin haaiza Namaz se door rahen. wo khair w barkat aur musalmanon ki dua mein Sharik hon. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham mein se kisi aurat ke paas chadar nahi hoti . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uski (koi musalman) behan usko apni chadar ka aik hissey pehna de."
2057,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Adi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-azha ya eidul-fitr ke din bahar nikley aur 2 rakatein padhaain, us se pahley ya baad mein koi Namaz nahi padhi. phir aurton ke paas aaey jabke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sath they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton ko sadqey ka hukm diya to koi aurat apni baaliyan (Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein) dalti thi aur koi apna ( long wghaira ka khushbu daar ( haar dalti thi."
2058,Muhammad-bin Idrees aur ghandar donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath us ( uper zikr ki gaee hadis) ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
2059,Malik ne zamra bin Saeed Mazni se aur unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu Waqid Lesi (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-azha aur eidul-fitr mein kon si sura qirat farmatey they? to unhon-ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un donon mein sura ( ق وَالْقُرْ‌آنِ الْمَجِيدِ (aur sura ( اقْتَرَ‌بَتِ السَّاعَةُ وَانشَقَّ الْقَمَرُ‌ ( padha kartey they.
2060,"Fulaih ne zamra bin Saeed se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Waqid Lesi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya, Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se us barey mein puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne eid ki Namaz mein kya padha ? to maine kaha : ( اقْتَرَ‌بَتِ السَّاعَةُ (aur ( ق وَالْقُرْ‌آنِ الْمَجِيدِ ( ."
2061,"abu-Usama ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mere yahan tashrif laey jabke mere paas Ansar ki 2 bachchiyan thin aur Ansar ne jang Buaas mein jo ashaar aik doosrey ke muqaabley mein kahey they, unhein gaa rahi thin. kaha : wo koi gaaney waaliyaan na thin. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (unhein dekh kar) kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein shaitan ki awaz ( buland ho rahi ( hai? aur ye eid ke din hua tha. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abu-Bakar ! har qaum ke liye aik eid hai aur ye hamari eid hai."
2062,abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( riwayat ki aur is mein hai 2 bachchiyaan daf se khel rahi thin ( daf baja rahi thin)
2063,"Amr ne kaha ke ibne-Shahab ne unhein Urwa se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki (unhon-ne kaha (ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mere yahan tashrif laey jabke Mina ke dinon mein mere paas 2 bachchiyan gaa rahi thin aur daf bajaa rahi thin aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kapda odhey letey huey they, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne un donon ko daantaa . is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne aap se kapda hataya aur farmaya : Abu-Bakar! unhein chhodiye ke ye eid ke din hain. aur) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap mujhey apni chadar se chhipaaey huey they aur main habshiyon ko dekh rahi thi ke wo khel rahe they aur main kam umr ladki thi, zara andaza lagaao us ladki ka shauq kis qadr hoga jo khel ki shauqeen, nau (9) umr thi (wo kitni der khel dekhegi?)"
2064,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se aur unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere hujrey ke darwazey par khadey hain aur habshi apne chhotey nezon ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid mein khel ( mashaqqatein kar) rahe they. aur aap mujhey apni chadar se chhipaaey huey hain taake main unke kartab dekh sakun, phir aap meri khaatir khadey rahe yahan tak ke main hi hun jo wapas palti, andaza karo aik nai umr ki ladki ka shauq kis qadr hoga jo khel ki shauqeen ho ( kitni der tak khadi rahi hogi. ("
2065,"Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ghar mein) dakhil huey jabke mere paas 2 bachchiyaan jang Buaas ke ashaar buland awaz se suna rahi thin. aap bistar par let gaey aur apna chehra (doosri samt ( pher liya. iske baad Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey. to unhon-ne mujhey sarzanish ki aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mojudgi mein shaitan ki awaz? is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur Farmaya : unhein chhodiye jab un (Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ki tawajjoh hati to maine unko ishara kya aur wo chali gain aur Eid ka aik din tha, kaley log dhalon aur bhalon ke kartab dikha rahe they, to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se darkhast ki ya aap ne khud hi farmaya : dekhney ki khahish rakhti ho? maine kaha : ji haan. aap ne mujhey apne peechhey khada kar liya, mera rukhsar aap ke rukhsar par (lag raha) tha aur aap farma rahe they : aey arfada ke beto! (apna muzahira) jari rakho. yahan tak ke jab main uktaa gaee (to (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey liye kafi hai? maine kaha : ji haan. farmaya : to chali jao."
2066,"Jarir ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : habshi aa kar eid ke din masjid mein hathiyaaron ke sath uchhal kood rahe they, ( hathiyaron ka muzaahira kar rahe they) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya , maine apna sar aap ke kandhey par rakha aur unka khel ( kartab ( dekhney lagi (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey rahe ( yahan tak ke maine khud hi unke khel ke nazaarey se wapsi ikhtiyar ki."
2067,Yahya bin Zakariya-bin abi Zayda aur Muhammad-bin-Bishr donon ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah) riwayat ki aur unhon-ne ( في المسجد ( (masjid mein) ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye.
2068,"Ata ne bataya ke mujhey Ubaid-bin-Umair ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke unhon-ne khelney walon ke barey mein kaha : main unka khel dekhnaa chahti hun. kaha : is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho gaey aur main darwazey par khadi ho kar aap ke kanon aur kandhon ke darmyan se dekhney lagi aur wo log masjid mein khel rahe they. Ata ne kaha : wo Irani they ya habshi aur kaha : mujhey ibne-Atiq yani Ubaid-bin-Umair ne bataya ke wo habshi they."
2069,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : jabke habshi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney apne bhaalon se khel rahe they, to Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) pahunch gaey aur kankariyaan uthaney ke liye jhukey taake wo unhein kankariyaan maarein to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : umr ! unhein chhod do."
